Package: RSMsoil
Title: Response Surface Methodology for Soil Fertility Assessment
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jardel", "Fialho", , "jardelllfialho@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements comprehensive Response Surface Methodology (RSM) analysis
    for soil fertility assessment, following the methodology of Victor Hugo Alvarez V.
    (2008). Includes first and second-order polynomial models, canonical analysis,
    path of steepest ascent/descent, and interactive visualization of response surfaces.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
